data.description: This enchanting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in the highly sought-after Wild Rose subdivision, offering a generous 1,861 heated sq. ft of living space. The kitchen is a chef's dream with stainless steel appliances, seamlessly blending modern convenience with classic charm.  Adjacent to the inviting family room is a spacious sunroom, perfect for soaking in natural light and enjoying tranquil moments. Step outside into your backyard oasis, ideal for entertaining guests with a pergola, outdoor fire pit, above-ground pool, and a 200 sq ft outbuilding, all set on a .36-acre lot.  Convenience meets comfort as this home is only minutes away from downtown Conway, where you can indulge in local cuisine, explore charming shops, and immerse yourself in entertainment options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this dreamy retreat yours. Contact us today for a private viewing.
